{"tid":154221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毆打兼恐嚇司機囚半年 向華強幼子上訴失敗即入獄","createTime":"2017-03-13T06:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T00:54:22.000Z","uid":5195,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"521c5654d59e4967e0986ee0440d0dd601b99f3f","tid":154221,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"電影商人向華強的幼子向佑，前年9月因不滿的士司機不識路，毆打司機兼自稱是向華強的兒子，「即係全香港最大家族嘅龍頭大佬」。向佑及後被裁定3罪罪成判囚半年，他去年11月提上訴，法官今頒下判詞，裁定向佑就定罪及刑期的上訴均失敗，一直保釋的他須即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n向佑（28歲）去年7月被裁定襲擊致造成身體傷害、刑事恐嚇及普通襲擊罪成。"},{"pid":"b0e880448ffcbfdcf252af600bc6be3b96018712","tid":154221,"uid":75,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6b7ce074031587d042cb3906a0e970238928ec","tid":154221,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9c5a2655ff9df1beddb2bf29bb391b3ea7e40e","tid":154221,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"要唔要叫黑"},{"pid":"ae74659e80579ea9fe61606440472491d6dc0d48","tid":154221,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"要唔要黑警畀返安家費畀向生"},{"pid":"4329cd72a9d842b0a08da0af059d81052540e001","tid":154221,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"等睇7警同樣上訴失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea8a01b